  "texts": [
    "I. INTRODUCTIONOne of the most significant applications of Deep Learning (DL) and Artificial Intelligence (AI) is image classification.",
    "The process of labeling images based on specific characteristics or features is known as image classification.",
    "These characteristics are discovered by the algorithm, which makes use of them to classify and differentiate between various images [1].The process of classifying images is known as image classification.",
    "This is accomplished by utilizing similar features found in images belonging to various classes to identify and label the images [2].",
    "Neural networks are useful in categorizing images, and DL algorithms utilize them as the core mechanism."
  ],
